---
import PostLayout from '@layouts/PostLayout.astro';
import CodeBlockInputCell from '@components/CodeBlockInputCell.astro';
import CodeBlockOutputCell from '@components/CodeBlockOutputCell.astro';

const { metadata_page } = await import('@portfolio/consts.json');
const { colors } = await import('@portfolio/consts.json');
const { svg_paths } = await import('@portfolio/consts.json');

const page_title = 'Formatador de código Black';
const end_url = 'tips/black';
const description = 'Seu colega Filipao está escrevendo código que é difícil de ler? Compartilhe com ele este formatador de código que eu mostro neste post! Venha e aprenda a formatar o código para torná-lo mais compreensível. Não vamos resolver os problemas de Filipao, mas pelo menos você não sofrerá ao lê-lo';
const keywords = 'black, formateador de código, pep8, python, legibilidad de código, mantenimiento de código, estilo de código, guía de estilo de código';
const languaje = 'PT';
const image_path = 'https://images.maximofn.com/black_formater_thumbnail.webp';
const opening_brace = '{';
const closing_brace = '}';
---

<PostLayout 
    title={page_title}
    languaje={languaje}
    description={description}
    keywords={keywords}
    author={metadata_page.author}
    theme_color={colors.background_color}
    end_url={end_url}
    image_path={image_path}
    image_width=500
    image_height=500
    image_extension=webp
    article_date=2024-10-29+T00:00:00Z
>

  <section class="post-body">


    <aside class="post-index">
      <a class="anchor-link" href="#Instala%C3%A7%C3%A3o"><h2>Instalação</h2></a>
      <a class="anchor-link" href="#Exemplo-de-c%C3%B3digo"><h2>Exemplo de código</h2></a>
      <a class="anchor-link" href="#Formatando-o-c%C3%B3digo"><h2>Formatando o código</h2></a>
    </aside>


    <div class="post-body-content">
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h1 id="Formatador-de-c%C3%B3digo-Black">Formatador de código Black<a class="anchor-link" href="#Formatador-de-c%C3%B3digo-Black"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 8" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h1>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <blockquote>
      <p>Aviso: Este post foi traduzido para o português usando um modelo de tradução automática. Por favor, me avise se encontrar algum erro.</p>
      </blockquote>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Se você já programou em Python por um tempo, suponho que conheça o <a href="https://peps.python.org/pep-0008/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">PEP8</a>, que é um guia de estilo para a escrita de código em Python, <a href="https://black.readthedocs.io/en/stable/">Black</a></p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Pois hoje trago um formatador de código Python que segue o <code>PEP8</code> de maneira que seus códigos sejam mais legíveis e manteníveis tanto por outros como pelo seu eu do futuro.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h2 id="Instala%C3%A7%C3%A3o">Instalação<a class="anchor-link" href="#Instala%C3%A7%C3%A3o"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 9" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Para instalá-lo podemos instalá-lo com conda</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>conda<span class="w"> </span>install<span class="w"> </span>conda-forge::black
      </pre></div>
      <p>o com pip</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>pip<span class="w"> </span>install<span class="w"> </span>black
      </pre></div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h2 id="Exemplo-de-c%C3%B3digo">Exemplo de código<a class="anchor-link" href="#Exemplo-de-c%C3%B3digo"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 10" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Vou criar um arquivo chamado <code>sample_code.py</code> com o seguinte código</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">myClass</span><span class="p">:</span>
      <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">display_info</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">subname</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">age</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">description</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">address</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">city</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">zip_code</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">country</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">phone</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">email</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">license</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">departament</span><span class="p">):</span>
      <span class="k">return</span> <span class="sa">f</span><span class="s2">"Name : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Subname : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">subname</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Age : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">age</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Description : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">description</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Address : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">address</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, City : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">city</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Zip Code : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">zip_code</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Country : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">country</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Phone : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">phone</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Email : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">email</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, License : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">license</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Departament : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">departament</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">"</span>
      
          <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">add_numbers</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num1</span><span class="p">,</span>
                          <span class="n">num2</span><span class="p">):</span>
              <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">num1</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">num2</span>
      
          <span class="n">text</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"This is some text"</span>
      
          <span class="n">letters</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span>
              <span class="s2">"alpha"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"beta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"gamma"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"delta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"epsilon"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"zeta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"eta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"theta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"iota"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"kappa"</span><span class="p">,</span>
          <span class="p">)</span>
      </pre></div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Como vemos, possui as duas primeiras linhas muito longas, a declaração do segundo método em várias linhas, etc.</p>
      <p><img decoding="async" onerror="this.parentNode.removeChild(this)" alt="olhos" src="https://images.maximofn.com/eyes.webp" width="272" height="185"/></p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h2 id="Formatando-o-c%C3%B3digo">Formatando o código<a class="anchor-link" href="#Formatando-o-c%C3%B3digo"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 11" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Para formatar o código temos duas opções, fazer</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>black<span class="w"> </span><span class="o">{opening_brace}</span>source_file_or_directory<span class="o">{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      <p>o fazer</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>python<span class="w"> </span>-m<span class="w"> </span>black<span class="w"> </span><span class="o">{opening_brace}</span>source_file_or_directory<span class="o">{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Assim, vamos formatá-lo</p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="o">!</span>black<span class="w"> </span>sample_code.py',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '<span class="ansi-bold">reformatted sample_code.py</span>',
          '<span class="ansi-bold">All done! ✨ 🍰 ✨</span>',
          '<span class="ansi-blue-intense-fg ansi-bold">1 file </span><span class="ansi-bold">reformatted</span>.',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Depois de formatá-lo, o código ficou assim</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">myClass</span><span class="p">:</span>
          <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">display_info</span><span class="p">(</span>
              <span class="bp">self</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">subname</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="n">age</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">description</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="n">address</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">city</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">zip_code</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">country</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">phone</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">email</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">license</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">departament</span><span class="p">,</span>
          <span class="p">):</span>
      <span class="k">return</span> <span class="sa">f</span><span class="s2">"Name : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Subname : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">subname</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Age : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">age</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Description : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">description</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Address : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">address</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, City : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">city</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Zip Code : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">zip_code</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Country : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">country</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Phone : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">phone</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Email : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">email</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, License : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">license</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">, Departament : </span><span class="si">{opening_brace}</span><span class="n">departament</span><span class="si">{closing_brace}</span><span class="s2">"</span>
      
          <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">add_numbers</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num2</span><span class="p">):</span>
              <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">num1</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">num2</span>
      
          <span class="n">text</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"This is some text"</span>
      
          <span class="n">letters</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span>
              <span class="s2">"alpha"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"beta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"gamma"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"delta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="n">epsilon</span>
              <span class="s2">"zeta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
      <span class="s2">"eta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"theta"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"iota"</span><span class="p">,</span>
              <span class="s2">"kappa"</span><span class="p">,</span>
          <span class="p">)</span>
      </pre></div>
      <p>Muito melhor, não é?</p>
      </section>
      






    </div>

  </section>

</PostLayout>
